   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sponsor an IDP Child</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project presents the opportunity to sponsor an IDP child, living in a garbage dump in Bamako, Mali. The program works in tandem with our project to &quot;Help Relocate 500 Children out of a Garbage Dump&quot; (Project # 24187). These children are living in poverty under the most deplorable conditions. They are lacking in food security, healthcare, hygiene, sanitation safety and education. Through this program you can sponsor a child and give them hope for their future.</narrative>
  </description>
